LORD ELDER shook his head, &quot;Who know why the Matrix chose Tuscon or
any of the other Primes for that matter?&quot; ELDER said in thoughtful
tones. &quot;But you may already know that not all Primes have a shard of
the Matrix, like Optimus Primal. Then again there have been those who
never had the title Prime who carried the Matrix, like Ultra Magnus or
even Alpha Trion.&quot;

He sighed, &quot;It may just have been that the Matrix realized that there
was no Prime at the time and knew that there needed one.&quot;

Gesturing broadly again LORD ELDER continued shook his head, &quot;But is
niether here nor there. In any case, I have explained to you at least
some of the history of the Earth, the last section is, that the
Watchers who were tasked with observing the Earth were now tasked with
watching the Minions - watching for any sign of Unicronian activity.
We were based in the Antarctic in a tower called Cryonosis.&quot;

LORD ELDER frowned slightly, &quot;It is this base, which was connected to
a satalite that we had in space that allowed us keep track of the
Minions and even to a lesser extent the Predacons.&quot;

He looked up at POLAR CLAW, RAMULUS, WOLFGANG, PROWL and finally at
NIGHTSHIFT, &quot;What none of you may know is that recently we . . . I . .
. have lost contact with the base and the satalite. We are blind as to
what is going on with the minions or anything else for that matter.&quot;

